获取所有组
GET /v3/groups
创建一个组
POST /v3/groups
-d {"group": {"description": "Contract developers","domain_id": "default","name": "Contract developers"}}
获取单个组
GET /v3/groups/{group_id}
更新单个组
PATCH /v3/groups/{group_id}
-d {"group": {"description": "Contract developers 2016","name": "Contract developers 2016"}}
删除单个组
DELETE /v3/groups/{group_id}
获取单个组中的所有用户
GET /v3/groups/{group_id}/users
更新单个组中的单个用户(添加用户到一个组里面)
PUT /v3/groups/{group_id}/users/{user_id}
检查一个用户是不是在组里
HEAD /v3/groups/{group_id}/users/{user_id}
移除单个组中单个用户
DELETE /v3/groups/{group_id}/users/{user_id}
